{{bottom}}

===Transitive===
'''to cease''' (''present participle'' '''[[ceasing]]''', past tense and past 
participle '''[[ceased]]''')

# (''formal'') To stop doing (something).
#:''And with that, he ceased [[twitch]]ing.''
